      Description copied from interface: IAnimatedArchitectureEventFactory
      Constructs a IStructureEventTogglePrepare.
      Specified by:
      createTogglePrepareEvent in interface IAnimatedArchitectureEventFactory
      Parameters:
      snapshot - The snapshot of the structure.
      cause - What caused the action.
      actionType - The type of action.
      responsible - Who is responsible for this structure. Either the player who directly toggled it (via a command or the GUI), or the original creator when this data is not available.
      time - The number of seconds the structure will take to open. Note that there are other factors that affect the total time as well.
      skipAnimation - If true, the structure will skip the animation and open instantly.
      newCuboid - The Cuboid representing the area the structure will take up after the toggle.
